					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To quote wikipedia...<br /><br />&quot;Contrary to popular belief, the Windows system API accepts slash, and thus all the above Unix examples should work. But many applications on Windows interpret a slash for other purposes or treat it as an invalid character, and thus require you to enter backslash — notably the cmd.exe shell&quot;<br /><br />That being said, I think I use forward slashes even on Windows, except in the command line.</div>

					
